<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:55:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>感知中“未完成”的自发优先顺序：视觉蔡加尼克效应</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-spontaneous-prioritization-of-unfinishedness-in-perception-a-visual-zeigarnik-effect</link><description>以特别持久的方式占据我们思想的事件往往是那些未完成的事件——从写了一半的论文到展开的衣服。这些事件似乎在记忆中也有优势，就像“蔡加尼克效应”一样：当人们执行各种任务，但有些任务由于外部干扰而从未完成时，对于那些未完成的任务，记忆往往会更好。但精神生活中的这种“未完成”到底有多重要呢？蔡加尼克效应通常通过诉诸目标的显着性或义务的重量来解释，但即使在独立于这些高级社会/动机因素的视觉处理中，未完成也可能自发地被优先考虑吗？通过四个实验（ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-spontaneous-prioritization-of-unfinishedness-in-perception-a-visual-zeigarnik-effect.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:55:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-spontaneous-prioritization-of-unfinishedness-in-perception-a-visual-zeigarnik-effect</guid></item><item><title>人类汉坦病毒：临床方面和管理的回顾</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hantavirus-in-humans-a-review-of-clinical-aspects-and-management</link><description>汉坦病毒感染是病毒性出血热大类的一部分。它们也被认为是全球分布的突发人畜共患感染的独特模型。影响其流行病学和传播的因素有很多，如气候、环境、社会发展、啮齿动物宿主的生态以及流行地区的人类行为。通过接触流行地区受感染的啮齿动物而传播给人类；然而，安第斯山脉汉坦病毒的独特之处在于它可以在人与人之间传播。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hantavirus-in-humans-a-review-of-clinical-aspects-and-management2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hantavirus-in-humans-a-review-of-clinical-aspects-and-management</guid></item><item><title>FDA 批准治疗 T2D 的新型每周基础胰岛素</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/fda-approves-novel-weekly-basal-insulin-for-t2d</link><description>FDA 已批准每周一次的胰岛素 icodec-abae（Awiqli；诺和诺德）用于治疗 2 型糖尿病 (T2D) 成人患者，目前预计下半年将推出 20,261 支 700 单位/mL 剂量的胰岛素。这种新颖的治疗方案是同类首创的治疗方法，使 T2D 患者摆脱了每日基础胰岛素注射的严格时间表，并将每 7 天的总注射次数从 7 次减少到 1 次。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fda-approves-novel-weekly-basal-insulin-for-t2d.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/fda-approves-novel-weekly-basal-insulin-for-t2d</guid></item><item><title>为什么多元宇宙可能是真实的</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-the-multiverse-could-be-real</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 01:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-the-multiverse-could-be-real</guid></item><item><title>冯诺依曼探测器：可以吞噬银河系的自我复制机器人</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/von-neumann-probes-the-self-replicating-robots-that-could-consume-the-galaxy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:55:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/von-neumann-probes-the-self-replicating-robots-that-could-consume-the-galaxy</guid></item><item><title>这个人形机器人的问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-problem-with-this-humanoid-robot</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-problem-with-this-humanoid-robot</guid></item><item><title>强化学习环境的终极指南：在法学硕士时代构建和扩展它们，作者：AdithyaSK</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-ultimate-guide-to-rl-environments-building-and-scaling-them-in-the-llm-era-by-adithyask</link><description>“任务”实际上包含什么？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-ultimate-guide-to-rl-environments-building-and-scaling-them-in-the-llm-era-by-adithyask3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-ultimate-guide-to-rl-environments-building-and-scaling-them-in-the-llm-era-by-adithyask</guid></item><item><title>没有公式：为什么人工智能无法解决最重要的问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/there-is-no-formula-why-ai-cannot-solve-what-matters-most</link><description>爱情没有公式。没有意义的公式。伟大的艺术、悲伤、重要的生活都没有公式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/there-is-no-formula-why-ai-cannot-solve-what-matters-most2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/there-is-no-formula-why-ai-cannot-solve-what-matters-most</guid></item><item><title>量子纠缠天空</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-entangles-the-heavens</link><description>随着美国、欧洲和中国竞相塑造地月走廊的未来，战略优势不仅取决于发射能力或月球基础设施，还取决于量子技术的进步。正如安全系统对地球至关重要一样，卫星和天基系统也支撑着从金融交易和导航到科学发现和机密军事任务等高价值、高影响力的行动。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-entangles-the-heavens.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 23:55:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-entangles-the-heavens</guid></item><item><title>复杂系统和大脑：从网络到动力学和功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/complex-systems-and-the-brain-from-networks-to-dynamics-and-function</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 23:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/complex-systems-and-the-brain-from-networks-to-dynamics-and-function</guid></item></channel></rss>